name: petStar_art.02 - New Wing
description:
cool ! a new interactive wing of the gallery is open. curated art (and music too)

While this kind of art is... not for everyone... the brightest, and most creative thinkers can see whats abstracted within these works. They tell a narrative as long as any novel. If you're not quite sure, look closer. You have to see whats *not* on the canvas. 

Well we said it's not for everyone.. but the crowd at the gallery speaks for itself..
